Support System.
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Basic proof of concept style Rails 3.1 application for tracking issues. So far I have made the basic framework and added styles taken from Bootstrap (http://twitter.github.com/bootstrap/).

Should be as simple as:

1. git clone git://github.com/dannymcc/Support-System.git
2. bundle install && rake db:migrate
3. rails s

Basic screenshot of v0.01 - http://cl.ly/0i1W1o463d2T2s0S2n0c